    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《静府:刺眼》是一款以女性为主视角、由鼠标操作的指向点击式2D独立游戏，其包含了密室逃脱、解谜、猎奇、怪诞、灵异、惊悚等等元素。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为女警，莫名魂穿到了一座诡秘府院之中。静寂悚然的小院，身形可怖的尸体，格格不入的物什，似曾相识的怨灵……冥冥中似乎有一股天意让人无法后退。推开院门，剖解迷局，逃脱此地，或许，还会了解到更为幽远的秘事，一切才刚刚开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras/aa7c4de8246a609dda73c123dc6b7b16.avif?t=1762400679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras_big/aa7c4de8246a609dda73c123dc6b7b16.avif?t=1762400679 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掠杀、庇护，静寂的府邸下暗流涌动； <br>仇恨、珍爱，苦痛的心脏中光明永存。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>贯穿几代女性的存亡故事，讲述生命的挣扎与不屈。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras/3d50ee3a18a97b306222f3d1b02fbfb5.avif?t=1762400679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras_big/3d50ee3a18a97b306222f3d1b02fbfb5.avif?t=1762400679 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冷硬而和润，<br>渺远却了然。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>利用雅致幽深的美术音乐，烘托别有意境的独特氛围。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u> </u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras/c02f506a691840fc8642a4e188461363.avif?t=1762400679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras_big/c02f506a691840fc8642a4e188461363.avif?t=1762400679 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外能无力，<br>内念长存。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>透过个性鲜明的人物角色，与其红尘际遇产生心灵共鸣。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras/b69481cd364f3be16fad68eb811e1fdd.avif?t=1762400679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144080/extras_big/b69481cd364f3be16fad68eb811e1fdd.avif?t=1762400679 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丝丝缠连，环环相扣，<br>一切答案尽存于心中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>打造易于上手的点击式冒险机制，操作鼠标去解开一连串的谜题。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
